These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Beverage: fanta, hot-chocolate, tea, 7up
Nationality: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
2. Beverage:fanta == Nationality:turkish##1
3. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
4. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Beverage:7up is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | 7up | tea | hot-chocolate | fanta   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
City: london, edinburgh, berlin, paris
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. City:paris == Sport:soccer##1
2. City:london is on the far right##1
3. City:edinburgh is on the right of City:paris##1
4. City:paris is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| City   | berlin | paris | edinburgh | london    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
City: new-york, paris, rome, prague
Movie-Genre: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
2. City:new-york == Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of City:prague##1
5. City:rome is on the left of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| City         | new-york | prague | rome   | paris |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

