.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
Movie-Genre: action, disaster, drama, western
House: cape-cod, modern, futuristic, farmhouse
1. House:modern == Movie-Genre:western##1
2. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the left of House:futuristic##1
3. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the left of Movie-Genre:action##1
4. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the right of Movie-Genre:western##1
5. House:cape-cod is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| House         | modern | farmhouse   | futuristic | cape-cod |

