.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Nationality: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
Music-Genre: folk, indie, country, punk
1. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
2. Music-Genre:indie is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Music-Genre:punk##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Music-Genre     | country  | folk    | indie       | punk |

 